OL,3,CTreasury must fully fund public sector
OL,4,Ctax increase, insists Robison
OL,6,FIt is "vital" the UK Government fully
OL,7,Ffunds the cost of a tax increase on
OL,8,Fthe public sector in Scotland, Finance
OL,9,FSecretary Shona Robison said as she
OL,10,Fcalled for clarity.
OL,12,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced a
OL,13,Fhike in employers' national insurance
OL,14,Fcontributions in her Budget last week,
OL,15,Fand pledged to cover the increases in
OL,16,Fthe public sector in England.
