OL,3,CTreasury must fully fund public sector
OL,4,Ctax increase, insists Robison
OL,6,F"We have broadly welcomed the UK
OL,7,FGovernment's autumn Budget as a step
OL,8,Fin the right direction, however one
OL,9,Fglaring issue is the pressure that the
OL,10,Fincrease of employer national
OL,11,Finsurance contributions have on
OL,12,Ffunding for Scotland's public
OL,13,Fservices," she said.
