OL,3,CTreasury must fully fund public sector
OL,4,Ctax increase, insists Robison
OL,6,F"We will be publishing our Budget for
OL,7,F2025-26 in just 31 days, and without a
OL,8,Fguarantee the national insurance costs
OL,9,Fwill be fully met by the UK
OL,10,FGovernment, we face a financial hole
OL,11,Fof up to #500 million that could see
OL,12,Ffunding diverted from frontline
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,F"We have a range of public sector
OL,16,Femployers, including the NHS, police
OL,17,Fand local authorities, who need
OL,18,Fclarity on this to inform their
OL,19,Fspending decisions.
