OL,3,CTreasury must fully fund public sector
OL,4,Ctax increase, insists Robison
OL,6,F"Scotland has a proportionately larger
OL,7,Fpublic sector than England, and higher
OL,8,Flevels of public sector pay.
OL,10,F"It is vital the Treasury fully funds
OL,11,Fthe actual costs in Scotland's public
OL,12,Fsector, and doesn't just give a much
OL,13,Flower value Barnett share of spending
OL,14,Fin England."
OL,16,FSpeaking during First Minister's
OL,17,FQuestions on Thursday, John Swinney
OL,18,Falso raised the issue in response to
OL,19,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar,
OL,20,Fdescribing it as "a #500 million
OL,21,Fquestion".
